name: Roy Tang
text: Merong TIEs that are jump-capable. Notably, Vader's TIE at the battle of yavin was jump capable (allowing him to survive the death star destruction). Also, when Finn and Poe escape in a TIE at the start of TFA, he expects the TIE to be able to jump away from Jakku, IDK if that means First Order TIEs are more advanced in general
